<header id="top" class="header alwaysShow">
    <div class="text-vertical-center logoTopPad">
        <div id="contentBox" class="contentBoxNoBackground">
            <img id="logo" src="/img/logosmall.png" alt="" />
        </div>
        <div class="contentBoxNoBackground">
            <p>&nbsp;<br /></p>
            <h2 class="headerText">Welcome</h2>
            <p class="headerText">We are delighted to invite you to the wedding of Hazel and Chris on 7th April 2018.</p>
            <p class="headerText">Please use the menu above or scroll down to view essential information on location and accommodation and to let us know if you can make it.</p>
            <p class="headerText">To allow for appropriate preparations, we request that you reply by the 1st January 2018.</p>

