                <p>Bisham Abbey National Sports Centre has around 50 newly built rooms for sports clubs. Guests can book these rooms, but we do not have exclusivity on occupancy, so they may sell out.</p>
                <p><b>Cost (pr/pn):</b> Double - £86. Single - £70. Child bed - £15. Cots £10 </p>
                <p><b>Location:</b>Onsite</p>
                <p><b>Note:</b> Child beds can only put in two of the rooms. We have reserved these rooms, so let us know if you need one.</p>
