                <p>A Premiere Inn located just the other side of Marlow Bridge as part of the George and Dragon pub.</p>
                <p><b>Cost (pr/pn):</b> At time of writing (October 17): £96 for a double room</p>
                <p><b>Location:</b>Just over a mile from Bisham Abbey</p>
